Live singing with Karaoke Smart. Sing wherever you want and whenever you want. Choose your favorite songs and sing with high sound quality. Enjoy thousands of karaoke songs in special playlists for every moment and occasion. Karaoke Smart constantly adds trending songs to the catalog. Discover what s new! Be part of the ranking Have fun singing share your recording get followers and stand out in our community in Latin America. Stands out on the channel Sing and appear in our channel of featured recordings in Latin America. Create a duet Record yourself singing a part of a song so that others can complete it with you. Join a duet Choose your favorite song explore the invitations and complete a duet with another person. Create new music Create new versions of your favorite songs solo or with other singers. Sing on your TV Search Karaoke Smart on your TV and connect the mobile app to interact with your friends sending stickers like tomatoes and more!

Options menu at the bottom to improve navigation within the app. More powerful and intelligent search engine that segments by best result songs and artists according to the search. The Connect option has been updated for better interaction with the TV. In addition more stickers have been added to interact from your cell phone.
